Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.98,0:00:09.65,Default,,0,0,0,,你来接我了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.10,0:00:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,小虎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.85,0:00:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,那果然是个梦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.98,0:00:46.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我出门了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.15,0:00:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.32,0:00:54.22,Default,,0,0,0,,昨晚打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.66,0:02:37.41,Default,,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.53,0:02:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,祖母一直以来承蒙关照了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.99,0:02:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我是她的外孙女林香具矢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.91,0:02:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,会在这里暂住一段时间
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.54,0:02:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,原本没打算这么早过来的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.59,0:02:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,但工作那头一直在催我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.22,0:02:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,工作?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.72,0:02:59.59,Default,,0,0,0,,正在学厨中
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.10,0:03:01.39,Default,,0,0,0,,厨…师?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.93,0:03:04.39,Default,,0,0,0,,在汤岛一个叫「梅之实」的店里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.27,0:03:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,,这样啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.07,0:03:15.07,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起  挡到你了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.95,0:03:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.20,0:03:21.66,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.71,0:03:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,咦  小光走了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.96,0:03:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我还想介绍你来着
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.09,0:03:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我们打过招呼了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.59,0:03:42.39,Default,,0,0,0,,好像光我一人在讲话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.77,0:03:49.31,Default,,0,0,0,,完全说不上话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.35,0:03:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,一句话都…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.31,0:03:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,没法像样地…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.07,0:03:57.99,Comment,,0,0,0,,快走
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.16,0:04:02.03,Comment,,0,0,0,,我肯定不行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.24,0:04:04.49,Comment,,0,0,0,,做不到啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.45,0:04:05.74,Default,,0,0,0,,为何我总是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.12,0:04:08.37,Default,,0,0,0,,无法表达…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.54,0:04:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,想说的话呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.84,0:04:23.39,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.97,0:04:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,什么情况
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.14,0:04:29.39,Default,,0,0,0,,大清早的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.52,0:04:34.27,Default,,0,0,0,,早上好  怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.65,0:04:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,有点事儿
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.36,0:04:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,他啊  之前你提过的那家伙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.03,0:04:44.53,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.91,0:04:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.16,0:04:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.62,0:04:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.87,0:04:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,早
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.25,0:04:59.09,Default,,0,0,0,,刚才是什么情况
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.18,0:05:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,管他呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.97,0:05:07.93,Default,,0,0,0,,那么  开始今天的工作吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.89,0:05:10.85,Default,,0,0,0,,有不懂的地方就问我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.27,0:05:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,好的  谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.49,0:05:25.45,Default,,0,0,0,,机械语
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.19,0:05:56.69,Default,,0,0,0,,机械工学
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.11,0:06:42.73,Default,,0,0,0,,腻了!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.98,0:06:45.78,Default,,0,0,0,,这种工作还要一直做十年吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.32,0:06:48.45,Default,,0,0,0,,西冈你可能要用更多时间吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.87,0:06:51.99,Default,,0,0,0,,在那之前我要换个工作
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.25,0:06:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,话说之前
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.00,0:07:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我见了外甥  他说想要个手机
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.71,0:07:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,明明只是个小学生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.84,0:07:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,,现在的小鬼真是早熟啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.43,0:07:09.05,Default,,0,0,0,,「早熟」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.72,0:07:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.55,0:07:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,「早熟儿童」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.31,0:07:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,「早熟儿童」形容男女皆可
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.85,0:07:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,但「早熟少女」只能用于女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.69,0:07:20.77,Default,,0,0,0,,此中差别…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.27,0:07:25.24,Default,,0,0,0,,从我的话也能扯到这里?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.82,0:07:32.91,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么连我也要来帮忙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.16,0:07:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,「奔放的少女」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.41,0:07:38.25,Default,,0,0,0,,「野丫头」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.79,0:07:39.54,Default,,0,0,0,,「悍妇」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.21,0:07:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,「疯丫头」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.59,0:07:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,没办法  我就来帮你一把
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.44,0:08:01.27,Default,,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.94,0:08:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.82,0:08:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,不谢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.78,0:08:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,原来还真有适合编辞典的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.08,0:08:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,荒木先生和松本老师马上要过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.80,0:08:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,今天是月度例会啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.05,0:08:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,准备工作就由我来做
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.39,0:08:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,,马缔你就继续筛选词条吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.72,0:08:38.22,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.68,0:08:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,西冈你也一样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.69,0:08:41.39,Default,,0,0,0,,收到
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.40,0:08:43.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我去买茶点
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.49,0:08:52.91,Default,,0,0,0,,啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.87,0:08:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,这次又发的什么疯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.33,0:08:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,这张卡片有什么问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.00,0:09:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.37,0:09:01.79,Default,,0,0,0,,啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.42,0:09:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,今天早晨也没能好好回答
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.84,0:09:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我…
